{
  "body": "When hitting the escape key, the focus jumps to the search field, and this focus change scrolls the page all the way up. This is irritating when using the escape key to hide the ctrl+F search field (at least in Chrome, I can't speak for other browsers).\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce:\r\n\r\n1. Open Chrome.\r\n2. Go to https://docs.perl6.org/type/Signature\r\n3. Ctrl+F, \"role\".\r\n4. Escape to hide the ctrl+F search field.\r\n",
